true about being careful,

00:47:59.870 --> 00:48:03.750
you know, the, two feet of
sea level rise versus the 20.

00:48:03.750 --> 00:48:06.580
So more in my
resources, but the idea

00:48:06.580 --> 00:48:10.100
is to naturally frame the
discussion very early on.

00:48:10.100 --> 00:48:11.890
And it's shocking
how well that works.

