00:53:22.630 --> 00:53:25.180
there is a lot of scientists
that are telling us

00:53:25.180 --> 00:53:30.160
that in the net, going forward,
there are a lot of harmful side

00:53:30.160 --> 00:53:33.070
effects that the carbon
